ctcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"productcatalogservice->TiDB\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 调用 productcatalogservice 的延迟从正常 10547.94ms 增加到异常 9076.33ms，且 checkoutservice 调用 productcatalogservice 的 GetProduct 操作出现连接拒绝错误。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 调用 shippingservice 的 ShipOrder 操作延迟从正常 225.57ms 增加到异常 1127.0ms。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 checkoutservice 调用 cartservice 的 GetCart 操作延迟从正常 2495.93ms 增加到异常 7131.0ms。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend 调用 productcatalogservice 的 GetProduct 操作出现连接拒绝错误，状态码为 500。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice 依赖 TiDB，可能因 TiDB 连接问题导致 productcatalogservice 异常。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。以下是异常期间的关键发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"request\", \"response\", \"rrt\", \"io_util\", \"pod_processes\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes从1.0变化到2.0，同时request和response指标出现异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: 1.0→2.0 (p99_change_ratio: 0.6667), request: 3350.5→22.0 (median_change_ratio: 1.9739), response: 2849.0→19.0 (median_change_ratio: 1.9